{"type":null,"faqId":18655,"title":"作为modem连接电脑上","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s2{font-weight:bold;}\n.p1{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:justify;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕， &gt; </span><span class=\"s2\">设置</span><span>。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2.  </span><span>在“</span><span class=\"s2\">无线和网络</span><span>”区域，点击“</span><span class=\"s2\">更多&gt;移动网络共享&gt;USB共享网络</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3.  </span><span>选择“</span><span class=\"s2\">USB共享网络</span><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4.  </span><span>安装好驱动后（驱动程序可以通过Hisuite安装），在PC侧，右键点击“</span><span class=\"s2\">我的电脑</span><span>”，在弹出的菜单中选择“</span><span class=\"s2\">管理</span><span>”，界面会显示新的网卡设备。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">备注</span><span>：使用USB共享网络方式上网时必须打开数据连接，否则无法上网。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>如果PC上有无线网卡等，可以用手机开启WLAN热点，PC通过WLAN连接到手机上网（目前支持Windows操作系统）。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"1719","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1422260322000,"seriesProductName":"Cherry-CL10,CherryPlus-TL00,CherryPlus-TL00H,CherryPlus-TL00M,CherryPlus-TL10,CherryPlus-UL00,CherryPlus-UL10","visitedTimes":101,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}